# modelmock

## Installing dependencies

```shell
python3 -m pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## Development Guides

Run the unittest:

```shell
python3 tests/units
```

## Examples

Generates a list of Agents:

```shell
python3 tests/demo/random_agents.py
```

Generates a list of Contracts:

```shell
python3 tests/demo/random_contracts.py
```
